Program: Outlook
Title: Shot in the Taliban attack on Malala
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0104gj2
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 31 Oct 2012
Kainat Riaz tells Shaimaa Khalil (pictured) how she was injured in the Taliban attack on her friend Malala Yousafzai. Ranjit Bolt, a successful British playwright, reveals how he was almost ruined by a gambling addiction. And meet Super Makia, the reigning African wrestling champion. Image: Outlook presenter Shaimaa Khalil Show less